CreateItemGroupCommand:
1) Select 2 items, select two other items. Should these commands be merged?
2) Should CreateGroupCommands be undone, if the next action selects a single
element?
3) Should CreateGroupCommands be undone, if the next command is a
DeleteGroupCommand?
4) What happens, if there are two separate itemGroups? For instance, select 2
items and generate a itemGroup. Add another state. Create another group.
5) Highlight the states properly
6) bLastCommandItemGroup (undo, if no move event occurs)
7) lastSelectedItemGroup (DeleteItemGroupCommand, if there is a selection of
any other mode like STATE or TRANS)
